(9, 'App\\Models\\Admin', 2, 'created', 'App\\Models\\News', 11, '[]', '{\"title\":\"Du l\\u1ecbch T\\u00e2y Ninh: C\\u1ea9m nang t\\u1eeb A \\u0111\\u1ebfn Z\",\"slug\":\"du-lich-tay-ninh-cam-nang-tu-a-den-z\",\"content\":\"<p><strong>Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ti\\u1ec7n di chuy\\u1ec3n t\\u1eeb TP. H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh \\u0111i T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng di chuy\\u1ec3n t\\u1edbi T\\u00e2y Ninh b\\u1eb1ng xe bu\\u00fdt, xe kh\\u00e1ch ho\\u1eb7c ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ti\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\\u00ean, xe m\\u00e1y ho\\u1eb7c \\u00f4t\\u00f4 c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n s\\u1ebd thu\\u1eadn ti\\u1ec7n h\\u01a1n khi di chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m th\\u0103m quan. T\\u1eeb TP HCM, \\u0111i theo \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng Qu\\u1ed1c l\\u1ed9 22 qua \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u1eadn huy\\u1ec7n C\\u1ee7 Chi (TP HCM), Tr\\u1ea3ng B\\u00e0ng (T\\u00e2y Ninh), t\\u1edbi v\\u00f2ng xoay \\u0111o\\u1ea1n ng\\u00e3 ba th\\u1ecb tr\\u1ea5n G\\u00f2 D\\u1ea7u th\\u00ec r\\u1ebd v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng Qu\\u1ed1c l\\u1ed9 22B r\\u1ed3i th\\u1eb3ng ti\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ebfn T\\u00e2y Ninh.<\\/p><p>N\\u1ebfu mu\\u1ed1n b\\u1eaft xe kh\\u00e1ch t\\u1eeb TP HCM \\u0111\\u1ebfn T\\u00e2y Ninh, du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 xu\\u1ea5t ph\\u00e1t t\\u1eeb b\\u1ebfn xe An S\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u1edf huy\\u1ec7n H\\u00f3c M\\u00f4n r\\u1ed3i mua v\\u00e9 xe kh\\u00e1ch \\u0111i T\\u00e2y Ninh c\\u1ee7a nh\\u00e0 xe \\u0110\\u1ed3ng Ph\\u01b0\\u1edbc (028 3504 4999), gi\\u00e1 v\\u00e9 ch\\u1ec9 kho\\u1ea3ng 80.000 \\u2013 100.000 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng\\/l\\u01b0\\u1ee3t. C\\u00f2n v\\u1edbi xe bu\\u00fdt, du kh\\u00e1ch t\\u1edbi b\\u1ebfn xe ch\\u1ee3 B\\u1ebfn Th\\u00e0nh l\\u00ean xe s\\u1ed1 70-3 \\u0111i t\\u1edbi cu\\u1ed1i b\\u1ebfn l\\u00e0 M\\u1ed9c B\\u00e0i, sau \\u0111\\u00f3 \\u0111i ti\\u1ebfp chuy\\u1ebfn xe s\\u1ed1 05 \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ebfn b\\u1ebfn xe T\\u00e2y Ninh. T\\u1ed5ng chi ph\\u00ed cho hai tuy\\u1ebfn n\\u00e0y l\\u00e0 55.000 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng.<\\/p><p>&nbsp;<\\/p><p><strong>\\u0110\\u1ecba \\u0111i\\u1ec3m l\\u01b0u tr\\u00fa t\\u1ea1i T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n \\u1edf th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 T\\u00e2y Ninh th\\u01b0\\u1eddng t\\u1eadp trung nhi\\u1ec1u \\u1edf khu v\\u1ef1c g\\u1ea7n n\\u00fai B\\u00e0 \\u0110en tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1c con \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0110\\u1ea1i l\\u1ed9 30\\/4, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng CMT8,\\u2026 gi\\u00e1 ph\\u00f2ng dao \\u0111\\u1ed9ng t\\u1eeb 100.000 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 400.000 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng m\\u1ed9t \\u0111\\u00eam. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m c\\u1eafm tr\\u1ea1i tr\\u00ean n\\u00fai B\\u00e0 \\u0110en ng\\u1eafm b\\u00ecnh minh c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u b\\u1ea1n tr\\u1ebb y\\u00eau th\\u00edch du l\\u1ecbch b\\u1ee5i l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn.<\\/p><p>\\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t, n\\u1ebfu mu\\u1ed1n ngh\\u1ec9 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng sang ch\\u1ea3nh \\u1edf T\\u00e2y Ninh th\\u00ec kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ecf qua <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.ivivu.com\\/khach-san-tay-ninh\\/khach-san-vinpearl-tay-ninh?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\\\"><strong>kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n Vinpearl T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong><\\/a> 5 sao. T\\u1ecda l\\u1ea1c t\\u1ea1i \\u0111i\\u1ec3m giao c\\u1ee7a 3 tuy\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng huy\\u1ebft m\\u1ea1ch ngay trung t\\u00e2m, kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n Vinpearl T\\u00e2y Ninh \\u0111\\u00e3 tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh \\u201cn\\u00f3c nh\\u00e0\\u201d m\\u1edbi c\\u1ee7a th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 v\\u00e0 mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn v\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p kh\\u00e1c bi\\u1ec7t&nbsp; t\\u1ea1i T\\u00e2y Ninh.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/120194958_5489530111073145_9049468000254933182_n.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"120194958_5489530111073145_9049468000254933182_n\\\"><\\/figure><p>&nbsp;<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/120185230_5489530271073129_947726663658939175_o.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"120185230_5489530271073129_947726663658939175_o\\\"><\\/figure><p>T\\u00e1i hi\\u1ec7n ho\\u00e0n h\\u1ea3o phong c\\u00e1ch Ch\\u00e2u \\u00c2u \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng, kh\\u00f4ng gian b\\u00ean trong kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n Vinpearl T\\u00e2y Ninh l\\u1ea5y m\\u00e0u tr\\u1eafng l\\u00e0m ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ea1o, k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p h\\u00e0i h\\u00f2a c\\u00f9ng s\\u1eafc v\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng v\\u00e0 m\\u00e0u \\u0111en huy\\u1ec1n b\\u00ed. Ngay t\\u1ea1i ti\\u1ec1n s\\u1ea3nh sang tr\\u1ecdng, lobby bar hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i, l\\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng ly cocktail v\\u00e0 th\\u1ee9c u\\u1ed1ng m\\u1edbi m\\u1ebb\\u2026 s\\u1ebd l\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec3m d\\u1eebng ch\\u00e2n g\\u00e2y m\\u1ebfn th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng cho du kh\\u00e1ch ngay khi b\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0o kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/120270965_5489530614406428_448069582999732935_o.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"120270965_5489530614406428_448069582999732935_o\\\"><\\/figure><p>Kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n v\\u1edbi phong c\\u00e1ch ho\\u00e0ng gia ch\\u00e2u \\u00c2u, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf c\\u1ef1c k\\u1ef3 h\\u00e0i h\\u00f2a tinh x\\u1ea3o, k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p c\\u00f9ng n\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u00e0i tr\\u00ed t\\u1ec9 m\\u1ec9, t\\u1ea1o ra kh\\u00f4ng gian ngh\\u1ec9 tr\\u1ecdn v\\u1eb9n cho du kh\\u00e1ch.&nbsp; \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, chu\\u1ed7i d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 ti\\u1ec7n \\u00edch kh\\u00e9p k\\u00edn b\\u00ean trong kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn s\\u1ef1 h\\u00e0i l\\u00f2ng cho m\\u1ed7i du kh\\u00e1ch.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/120199064_5489530244406465_4349470807019733465_o.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"120199064_5489530244406465_4349470807019733465_o\\\"><\\/figure><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/120197581_5489530324406457_8182512914360964294_n.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"120197581_5489530324406457_8182512914360964294_n\\\"><\\/figure><p>T\\u1ea1i ph\\u00f2ng ngh\\u1ec9, du kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ph\\u00f3ng t\\u1ea7m m\\u1eaft bao qu\\u00e1t tr\\u1ecdn v\\u1eb9n khung c\\u1ea3nh c\\u1ee7a th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 bi\\u00ean gi\\u1edbi T\\u00e2y Ninh. T\\u1ea7m nh\\u00ecn tr\\u00ean cao \\u0111\\u1eaft gi\\u00e1 \\u0111\\u01b0a du kh\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u1ebfn v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t c\\u1ea3m quan tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n m\\u1edbi l\\u1ea1.<\\/p><p><strong>CLICK THAM KH\\u1ea2O NGAY&nbsp;<\\/strong><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.ivivu.com\\/khach-san-tay-ninh\\/khach-san-vinpearl-tay-ninh?utm_source=blog_ivivu&amp;utm_medium=post_link&amp;utm_campaign=internal\\\"><strong>KH\\u00c1CH S\\u1ea0N VINPEARL T\\u00c2Y NINH<\\/strong><\\/a><strong>&nbsp;V\\u1edaI GI\\u00c1 \\u01afU \\u0110\\u00c3I C\\u1ef0C T\\u1ed0T<\\/strong><\\/p><p><br><strong>Nh\\u1eefng \\u0111i\\u1ec3m check-in kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ecf qua khi \\u0111\\u1ebfn T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-haggg___.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu- haggg___\\\"><\\/figure><p><i>A\\u0309nh: @haggg___<\\/i><\\/p><p><strong>1. Nu\\u0301i Ba\\u0300 \\u0110en<\\/strong><\\/p><p>N\\u00fai B\\u00e0 \\u0110en n\\u1eb1m c\\u00e1ch th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 T\\u00e2y Ninh kho\\u1ea3ng 8km, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c bi\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ebfn nh\\u01b0 l\\u00e0 n\\u00f3c nh\\u00e0 c\\u1ee7a v\\u00f9ng Nam B\\u1ed9, v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ec9nh cao nh\\u1ea5t l\\u00e0 986m, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u00ecnh th\\u00e0nh b\\u1edfi ba ng\\u1ecdn n\\u00fai: n\\u00fai Heo, n\\u00fai Ph\\u1ee5ng, n\\u00fai B\\u00e0 \\u0110en. Nh\\u00ecn t\\u1eeb xa, ng\\u1ecdn n\\u00fai nh\\u01b0 m\\u1ed9t chi\\u1ebfc n\\u00f3n l\\u00e1 kh\\u1ed5ng l\\u1ed3 \\u0111ang n\\u1eb1m \\u00fap xu\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng ru\\u1ed9ng xanh t\\u01b0\\u01a1i bao la. Khung c\\u1ea3nh n\\u00ean th\\u01a1 \\u1ea5y c\\u00f9ng chi\\u1ec1u cao c\\u1ee7a n\\u00fai \\u0111\\u00e3 d\\u1ea7n tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh nguy\\u00ean nh\\u00e2n ch\\u00ednh m\\u00e0 nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u1ecdn leo n\\u00fai B\\u00e0 \\u0110en nh\\u01b0 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u1ec3 tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m nh\\u1eefng kho\\u1ea3nh kh\\u1eafc tuy\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1eb9p v\\u1edbi thi\\u00ean nhi\\u00ean trong chuy\\u1ebfn&nbsp;<i>du l\\u1ecbch T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/i>.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-nguyen.phan25121.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-nguyen.phan25121\\\"><\\/figure><p><i>A\\u0309nh: @nguyen.phan2512<\\/i><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-quyendowtothesoul.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-quyendowtothesoul\\\"><\\/figure><p><i>A\\u0309nh: @quyendowtothesoul<\\/i><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-1\\\"><\\/figure><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-2.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-2\\\"><\\/figure><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-3.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-3\\\"><\\/figure><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-4.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-4\\\"><\\/figure><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-5.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-5\\\"><\\/figure><p><strong>2. H\\u00f4\\u0300 \\u0110a\\u0301 Ma Thi\\u00ean La\\u0303nh<\\/strong><\\/p><p>H\\u1ed3 \\u0111\\u00e1 Ma Thi\\u00ean L\\u00e3nh hay c\\u00f2n g\\u1ecdi l\\u00e0 Thung L\\u0169ng Ma Thi\\u00ean L\\u00e3nh n\\u1eb1m ti\\u1ebfp gi\\u00e1p gi\\u1eefa ba ng\\u1ecdn n\\u00fai l\\u00e0 n\\u00fai B\\u00e0 \\u0110en, n\\u00fai Ph\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0 n\\u00fai Heo thu\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u1ecba b\\u00e0n x\\u00e3 Th\\u1ea1nh T\\u00e2n, t\\u1ec9nh T\\u00e2y Ninh. N\\u01a1i n\\u00e0y s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu khung c\\u1ea3nh r\\u1eebng nguy\\u00ean sinh tuy\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1eb9p \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c v\\u00ed nh\\u01b0 \\u201c\\u0110\\u00e0 L\\u1ea1t c\\u1ee7a mi\\u1ec1n \\u0110\\u00f4ng Nam B\\u1ed9\\u201d v\\u00e0 r\\u1ea5t \\u00edt kh\\u00e1ch<strong>&nbsp;du l\\u1ecbch T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong>&nbsp;bi\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ebfn.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-cchang2902.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-cchang2902\\\"><\\/figure><p><i>A\\u0309nh: @cchang2902<\\/i><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-tumcassie1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-tumcassie1\\\"><\\/figure><p><i>A\\u0309nh: @tumcassie<\\/i><\\/p><p><strong>3. H\\u00f4\\u0300 D\\u00e2\\u0300u Ti\\u00ea\\u0301ng<\\/strong><\\/p><p>M\\u1eb7t h\\u1ed3 quanh n\\u0103m xanh th\\u1eb3m, y\\u00ean \\u1ea3, c\\u1ecf m\\u1ecdc th\\u00e0nh th\\u1ea3m xanh m\\u01b0\\u1edbt xung quanh h\\u1ed3. Gi\\u1eefa l\\u00f2ng h\\u1ed3 m\\u1ecdc l\\u00ean c\\u00e1c \\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ea3o t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean l\\u1ea1 m\\u1eaft, \\u0111i\\u1ec3m xuy\\u1ebft th\\u00eam m\\u00e0u n\\u00e2u s\\u1eabm c\\u1ee7a nh\\u1eefng chi\\u1ebfc thuy\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u1ed9c m\\u1ed9c c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00e2n \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00f4i l\\u1eefng l\\u1edd\\u2026 \\u0110\\u1ebfn tham quan v\\u00e0o l\\u00fac b\\u00ecnh minh v\\u00e0 ho\\u00e0ng h\\u00f4n l\\u00e0 hai th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u1eb9p nh\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ec3 ng\\u1eafm c\\u1ea3nh n\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u00e2y, khi\\u1ebfn t\\u00e2m h\\u1ed3n ba\\u0323n c\\u1ea3m th\\u1ea5y say \\u0111\\u1eafm.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-th.__.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-th.__\\\"><\\/figure><p><i>A\\u0309nh: @th.__<\\/i><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-dhtlin.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-dhtlin\\\"><\\/figure><p><i>A\\u0309nh: @dhtlin<\\/i><\\/p><p><strong>4. To\\u0300a Tha\\u0301nh T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong><\\/p><p><i><strong>Du l\\u1ecbch T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong><\\/i>&nbsp;th\\u00ec kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 kh\\u00f4ng gh\\u00e9 qua T\\u00f2a Th\\u00e1nh, \\u0111\\u00e2y kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 l\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh mang \\u00fd ngh\\u0129a t\\u00e2m linh m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu ki\\u1ebfn tr\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o. Hai h\\u00e0ng c\\u1ed9t ph\\u00eda trong t\\u00f2a \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tr\\u1ea1m tr\\u1ed5 h\\u00ecnh r\\u1ed3ng v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u m\\u00e0u s\\u1eafc r\\u1ef1c r\\u1ee1. N\\u1ec1n t\\u00f2a th\\u00e1nh c\\u00f3 9 c\\u1ea5p \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c g\\u1ecdi l\\u00e0 \\u201cC\\u1eedu ph\\u1ea9m th\\u1ea7n ti\\u00ean\\u201d, m\\u1ed7i c\\u1ea5p t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t ph\\u1ea9m c\\u1ea5p. \\u1ede gi\\u1eefa c\\u00f3 qu\\u1ea3 c\\u1ea7u l\\u1edbn t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng tr\\u01b0ng cho v\\u0169 tr\\u1ee5 v\\u1edbi Thi\\u00ean Nh\\u00e3n n\\u1eb1m ph\\u00eda tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc. T\\u00f2a Th\\u00e1nh T\\u00e2y Ninh h\\u00e0ng n\\u0103m v\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u00f3n h\\u00e0ng ng\\u00e0n l\\u01b0\\u1ee3t du kh\\u00e1ch t\\u1edbi tham quan c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh c\\u1ef1c k\\u00ec \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o n\\u00e0y.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-anhtins_.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-anhtins_\\\"><\\/figure><p><i>A\\u0309nh: @anhtins_<\\/i><\\/p><p><strong>5. Tha\\u0301p Cho\\u0301p Ma\\u0323t<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Th\\u00e1p Ch\\u00f3p M\\u1ea1t l\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c B\\u1ed9 V\\u0103n h\\u00f3a Th\\u1ec3 thao v\\u00e0 Du l\\u1ecbch c\\u00f4ng nh\\u1eadn l\\u00e0 di t\\u00edch l\\u1ecbch s\\u1eed- v\\u0103n h\\u00f3a, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t trong ba c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh th\\u00e1p c\\u1ed5 cu\\u1ed1i c\\u00f9ng c\\u00f2n l\\u1ea1i \\u1edf mi\\u1ec1n Nam n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ta. To\\u00e0n b\\u1ed9 t\\u00f2a th\\u00e1p \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x\\u00e2y d\\u1eebng b\\u1eb1ng g\\u1ea1ch v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00e1 phi\\u1ebfn v\\u1edbi ph\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ec9nh th\\u00e1p nh\\u1ecdn d\\u1ea7n l\\u00ean, t\\u1eeb m\\u1eb7t \\u0111\\u1ea5t l\\u00ean n\\u01a1i cao nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ec9nh th\\u00e1p \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u00ednh l\\u00e0 10m.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-hoanghuyyy.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-hoanghuyyy\\\"><\\/figure><p><i>A\\u0309nh: @hoanghuyyy<\\/i><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-hoanghuyyy1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-hoanghuyyy1\\\"><\\/figure><p><strong>6. Kha\\u0301ch sa\\u0323n Vinpearl T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong><\\/p><p>&nbsp;Ngay khi v\\u1eeba m\\u1edbi ra m\\u1eaft, kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n Vinpearl Hotel T\\u00e2y Ninh \\u0111\\u00e3 ngay l\\u1eadp t\\u1ee9c tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u201cquy\\u1ebfn r\\u0169\\u201d nh\\u1ea5t n\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u1ea5t th\\u00e1nh T\\u00e2y Ninh. L\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00e2n v\\u00e0 du kh\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u1ebfn v\\u1edbi T\\u00e2y Ninh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn v\\u1edbi kh\\u00f4ng gian ngh\\u1ec9 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng sang tr\\u1ecdng, d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 \\u0111\\u1eb3ng c\\u1ea5p c\\u00f9ng chu\\u1ed7i ti\\u1ec7n \\u00edch h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u theo ti\\u00eau chu\\u1ea9n 5 sao qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-tranngocvu_.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-tranngocvu_\\\"><\\/figure><p><i>A\\u0309nh: @tranngocvu_<\\/i><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-tai.shenky.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-tai.shenky\\\"><\\/figure><p><i>A\\u0309nh: @tai.shenky<\\/i><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/07\\/co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-7.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"co-chac-tay-ninh-la-day-doi-gio-phuot-tay-ninh-check-in6-diem-den-dep-ngo-ngang-ivivu-7\\\"><\\/figure><p><strong>8. V\\u01b0\\u1eddn nho r\\u1eebng T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong><\\/p><p>T\\u1ecda l\\u1ea1c t\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ecba ch\\u1ec9 622 x\\u00e3 Phan, huy\\u1ec7n D\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Minh Ch\\u00e2u, t\\u1ec9nh T\\u00e2y Ninh, v\\u01b0\\u1eddn nho r\\u1eebng thu\\u1ed9c c\\u00f4ng ty s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t r\\u01b0\\u1ee3u vang Vang Cy \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c xem l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u1ebfn h\\u1ea5p d\\u1eabn nh\\u1ea5t T\\u00e2y Ninh. V\\u01b0\\u1eddn nho r\\u1eebng n\\u00e0y m\\u1edf c\\u1eeda \\u0111\\u00f3n kh\\u00e1ch tham quan, cho th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c nho v\\u00e0 u\\u1ed1ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nho mi\\u1ec5n ph\\u00ed.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/08\\/vuon-nho-tay-ninh-ivivu-3.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"vuon-nho-tay-ninh-ivivu-3\\\"><\\/figure><p>V\\u01b0\\u1eddn nho r\\u1eebng \\u1edf \\u0111\\u00e2y tr\\u00e1i ch\\u00edn m\\u1ecdc th\\u00e0nh ch\\u00f9m nh\\u01b0 nho th\\u01b0\\u1eddng, c\\u00f3 m\\u00e0u \\u0111en s\\u1eadm v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ec9 nh\\u1ecf b\\u1eb1ng qu\\u1ea3 c\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea. Ch\\u00f9m ch\\u00edn r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u qu\\u1ea3, n\\u1eb7ng kho\\u1ea3ng 2 kg. Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u1ee7 d\\u00e0nh m\\u1ed9t v\\u01b0\\u1eddn r\\u1ed9ng kho\\u1ea3ng 8.000 m2 kh\\u00f4ng thu ho\\u1ea1ch tr\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ec3 du kh\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u1ebfn tham quan mi\\u1ec5n ph\\u00ed.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/08\\/vuon-nho-tay-ninh-ivivu-2.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\u1ea2nh: Mi Mi \\\"><\\/figure><p><i>\\u1ea2nh: Mi Mi<\\/i><\\/p><p>\\u0110\\u1ebfn v\\u1edbi v\\u01b0\\u1eddn nho r\\u1eebng T\\u00e2y Ninh, c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tham quan mi\\u1ec5n ph\\u00ed, ch\\u1ee5p cho\\u1eb9t tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng ch\\u00f9m nho ch\\u00edn m\\u1ecdng, tr\\u0129u qu\\u1ea3.&nbsp; Ngo\\u00e0i ch\\u1ee5p h\\u00ecnh v\\u1edbi v\\u01b0\\u1eddn nho, c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c nho r\\u1eebng t\\u1ea1i ch\\u1ed7 lu\\u00f4n nha. L\\u01b0u \\u00fd, nho r\\u1eebng v\\u1ecb h\\u01a1i chua, \\u0103n nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u1ea7u l\\u01b0\\u1ee1i s\\u1ebd b\\u1ecb t\\u00ea n\\u00ean c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n \\u0103n \\u00edt cho bi\\u1ebft th\\u00f4i nh\\u00e9!<\\/p><p><i>H\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111i:<\\/i> T\\u1eeb S\\u00e0i G\\u00f2n c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111i tr\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng huy\\u1ec7n D\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Minh Ch\\u00e2u v\\u1ec1 h\\u01b0\\u1edbng n\\u00fai B\\u00e0 \\u0110en, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng DT784 \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u1ea7u K13, r\\u1ebd sang DT781, \\u0111\\u1ebfn tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng ti\\u1ec3u h\\u1ecdc x\\u00e3 Phan, \\u0111i th\\u00eam kho\\u1ea3ng 100m s\\u1ebd th\\u1ea5y b\\u1ea3ng Cty R\\u01b0\\u1ee3u Vang CY ph\\u00eda tay tr\\u00e1i.<br>&nbsp;<\\/p><h4><strong>C\\u00c1C M\\u00d3N \\u0110\\u1eb6C S\\u1ea2N \\u1ede T\\u00c2Y NINH KH\\u00d4NG TH\\u1ec2 B\\u1ece QUA<\\/strong><\\/h4><p><strong>B\\u00e1nh canh Tr\\u1ea3ng B\\u00e0ng<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Nh\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u1ecb tr\\u1ea5n Tr\\u1ea3ng B\\u00e0ng, trong l\\u00f2ng th\\u1ef1c kh\\u00e1ch xa g\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ec1u ngh\\u0129 \\u0111\\u1ebfn m\\u00f3n b\\u00e1nh canh g\\u1eafn li\\u1ec1n v\\u1edbi n\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u00e2y. T\\u00f4 b\\u00e1nh canh \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng v\\u1edbi gi\\u00f2 heo, huy\\u1ebft v\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng c\\u1ecdng h\\u00e0nh xanh t\\u01b0\\u01a1i, tuy \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n nh\\u01b0ng th\\u1ef1c kh\\u00e1ch ngay l\\u1eadp t\\u1ee9c b\\u1ecb cu\\u1ed1n h\\u00fat khi th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c qua. Kh\\u00f3i c\\u1ee7a t\\u00f4 b\\u00e1nh canh b\\u1ed1c nghi ng\\u00fat, l\\u0103n t\\u0103n m\\u1ee1 hoa n\\u00f3ng b\\u1ecfng khi h\\u00fap th\\u1eed. B\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd c\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c v\\u1ecb th\\u01a1m c\\u1ee7a h\\u00e0nh, v\\u1ecb cay c\\u1ee7a ti\\u00eau, v\\u1ecb ng\\u1ecdt c\\u1ee7a n\\u01b0\\u1edbc l\\u00e8o x\\u01b0\\u01a1ng h\\u1ea7m hay v\\u1ecb m\\u1ec1m c\\u1ee7a nh\\u1eefng l\\u00e1t th\\u1ecbt ph\\u00eda tr\\u00ean.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/banh-canh-trang-bang-ivivu.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"banh-canh-trang-bang-ivivu\\\"><\\/figure><p><strong>B\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng ph\\u01a1i s\\u01b0\\u01a1ng cu\\u1ed1n th\\u1ecbt<\\/strong><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/banh-trang-phoi-suong-trang-bang-ivivu.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"banh-trang-phoi-suong-trang-bang-ivivu\\\"><\\/figure><p>\\u0110\\u01b0\\u1ee3c xem l\\u00e0 m\\u00f3n \\u0111\\u1eb7c s\\u1ea3n c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00e2n Tr\\u1ea3ng B\\u00e0ng, b\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng ph\\u01a1i s\\u01b0\\u01a1ng c\\u00f3 quy tr\\u00ecnh ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn c\\u00f4ng phu, c\\u1ea7u k\\u1ef3 v\\u00e0 tinh t\\u1ebf. B\\u00e1nh ph\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u00e0m t\\u1eeb g\\u1ea1o ngon, kh\\u00f4ng pha tr\\u1ed9n. Khi xay g\\u1ea1o s\\u1ebd cho th\\u00eam m\\u1ed9t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng mu\\u1ed1i \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o v\\u1ecb m\\u1eb7n. B\\u00e1nh \\u0111em \\u0111i tr\\u00e1ng c\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 hai l\\u1edbp, d\\u00e0y h\\u01a1n so v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i kh\\u00e1c. Quy tr\\u00ecnh l\\u00e0m b\\u00e1nh \\u0111\\u00f2i h\\u1ecfi s\\u1ef1 kh\\u00e9o l\\u00e9o v\\u00e0 t\\u1ec9 m\\u1ec9, khi b\\u00e1nh ch\\u00edn s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111em \\u0111i ph\\u01a1i n\\u1eafng, n\\u01b0\\u1edbng tr\\u00ean m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1i l\\u00f2 \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi b\\u00e1nh chuy\\u1ec3n m\\u00e0u v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebfp \\u0111\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111em ph\\u01a1i s\\u01b0\\u01a1ng trong kho\\u1ea3ng th\\u1eddi gian nh\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ecbnh.<\\/p><p>B\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng ph\\u01a1i s\\u01b0\\u01a1ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0103n k\\u00e8m v\\u1edbi rau s\\u1ed1ng, th\\u1ecbt heo lu\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ea5m v\\u1edbi n\\u01b0\\u1edbc m\\u1eafm pha ch\\u1ebf c\\u00f4ng phu. B\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng m\\u1ec1m d\\u1ebbo v\\u1edbi l\\u00e1t th\\u1ecbt t\\u01b0\\u01a1i ngon h\\u00f2a c\\u00f9ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ch\\u1ea5m \\u0111\\u1eadm \\u0111\\u00e0, c\\u00f9ng v\\u1ecb ch\\u00e1t, chua c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i rau t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean m\\u00f3n \\u0103n tuy\\u1ec7t h\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u1ea7y l\\u00f4i cu\\u1ed1n.<\\/p><p><strong>&nbsp;B\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng me<\\/strong><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/banh-trang-me-ivivu.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"banh-trang-me-ivivu\\\"><\\/figure><p>T\\u1eeb b\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng ph\\u01a1i s\\u01b0\\u01a1ng, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00e2n n\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u00e2y s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o th\\u00eam nhi\\u1ec1u m\\u00f3n \\u0111i k\\u00e8m nh\\u01b0 b\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng tr\\u1ed9n, b\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng n\\u01b0\\u1edbng v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t c\\u00f3 m\\u00f3n b\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng me l\\u00e0m th\\u00e0nh m\\u00f3n \\u0111\\u1eb7c s\\u1ea3n \\u0103n v\\u1eb7t cu\\u1ed1n h\\u00fat nhi\\u1ec1u gi\\u1edbi tr\\u1ebb. M\\u00f3n \\u0103n g\\u1ed3m m\\u1ed9t \\u00edt b\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng ph\\u01a1i s\\u01b0\\u01a1ng, b\\u1ecbch m\\u1eafm me, h\\u00e0nh phi, \\u0111\\u1eadu ph\\u1ed9ng, b\\u1ed9t t\\u00f4m rang v\\u00e0 mu\\u1ed1i \\u1edbt \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u1ecf s\\u1eb5n trong b\\u1ecbch.<\\/p><p>T\\u00f9y theo s\\u1edf th\\u00edch th\\u1ef1c kh\\u00e1ch c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u00f9y nghi gia gi\\u1ea3m c\\u00e1c g\\u00f3i gia v\\u1ecb \\u0111i k\\u00e8m \\u0111\\u1ec3 pha th\\u00e0nh n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ch\\u1ea5m \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t. G\\u1ee1 c\\u00e1c mi\\u1ebfng b\\u00e1nh d\\u1ebbo dai s\\u1eb5n c\\u00f3, cu\\u1ed1n l\\u1ea1i ch\\u1ea5m v\\u1edbi ch\\u00e9n gia v\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t v\\u1eeba pha ch\\u1ebf v\\u00e0 ch\\u1eadm r\\u00e3i th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c. V\\u1ecb chua d\\u1ecbu c\\u1ee7a n\\u01b0\\u1edbc me, v\\u1ecb cay x\\u00e9 l\\u01b0\\u1ee1i c\\u1ee7a \\u1edbt, v\\u1ecb m\\u1eb7n c\\u1ee7a b\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng, v\\u1ecb th\\u01a1m c\\u1ee7a t\\u00f4m rang c\\u00f9ng v\\u1ecb b\\u00e9o gi\\u00f2n c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1eadu ph\\u1ed9ng t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean m\\u1ed9t h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng, quy\\u1ebfn r\\u0169 th\\u01a1m ngon \\u0111\\u1ebfn kh\\u00f3 t\\u1ea3.<\\/p><p><strong>\\u1ed0c xu n\\u00fai B\\u00e0<\\/strong><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/oc-nui-ba-ivivu.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"oc-nui-ba-ivivu\\\"><\\/figure><p>C\\u00f3 h\\u00ecnh d\\u1ea1ng g\\u1ea7n gi\\u1ed1ng \\u1ed1c b\\u01b0\\u01a1u nh\\u01b0ng c\\u00f3 m\\u00ecnh d\\u1eb9t v\\u00e0 nh\\u1ecf h\\u01a1n, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00e2n n\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u00e2y cho r\\u1eb1ng \\u1ed1c xu n\\u00fai B\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng nh\\u1eefng ngon \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n c\\u00f3 t\\u00e1c d\\u1ee5ng ch\\u01b0a nh\\u1ee9c m\\u1ecfi kh\\u00e1 t\\u1ed1t. \\u1ed0c b\\u1eaft v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn th\\u00e0nh nhi\\u1ec1u m\\u00f3n h\\u1ea5p d\\u1eabn nh\\u01b0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbng, h\\u1ea5p x\\u1ea3, x\\u00e0o me, x\\u00e0o t\\u1ecfi\\u2026 Th\\u1ecbt \\u1ed1c c\\u00f3 v\\u1ecb dai, gi\\u00f2n, v\\u1ecb ng\\u1ecdt thanh v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 ch\\u00fat h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng thu\\u1ed1c qu\\u00fd.<\\/p><p>\\u0110\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn v\\u1ecb ngon \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t c\\u1ee7a \\u1ed1c, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00e2n \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng khi b\\u1eaft \\u1ed1c n\\u00fai v\\u1ec1 th\\u01b0\\u1eddng cho c\\u01a1m d\\u1eeba n\\u1ea1o nhuy\\u1ec5n v\\u00e0o r\\u1ed3i h\\u1ea5p v\\u1edbi x\\u1ea3 hay g\\u1eebng v\\u00e0 gia v\\u1ecb ch\\u1ea5m \\u0111i k\\u00e8m l\\u00e0 mu\\u1ed1i ti\\u00eau chanh.<\\/p><p><strong>Th\\u1eb1n l\\u1eb1n n\\u00fai B\\u00e0 \\u0110en<\\/strong><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/than-lan-nui-ba-den-tay-ninh.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"than-lan-nui-ba-den-tay-ninh\\\"><\\/figure><p>\\u0110\\u01b0\\u1ee3c xem l\\u00e0 \\u201c\\u0111\\u1ec7 nh\\u1ea5t \\u1ea9m th\\u1ef1c\\u201d \\u1edf x\\u1ee9 T\\u00e2y Ninh, th\\u1eb1n l\\u1eb1n n\\u00fai l\\u00e0 m\\u00f3n nh\\u1eadu cu\\u1ed1n h\\u00fat c\\u00e1nh m\\u00e0y r\\u00e2u. M\\u00f3n \\u0103n n\\u00e0y lu\\u00f4n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u th\\u1ef1c kh\\u00e1ch s\\u0103n \\u0111\\u00f3n khi \\u0111\\u1ebfn T\\u00e2y Ninh.<\\/p><p>Th\\u1eb1n l\\u1eb1n n\\u00fai \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn th\\u00e0nh nhi\\u1ec1u m\\u00f3n nh\\u01b0 b\\u0103m nh\\u1ecf x\\u00e0o v\\u1edbi ti\\u00eau xanh \\u0103n k\\u00e8m b\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng v\\u00e0 l\\u00e1 l\\u1ed1t. Ngon nh\\u1ea5t ph\\u1ea3i k\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ebfn l\\u00e0 th\\u1eb1n l\\u1eb1n n\\u00fai chi\\u00ean gi\\u00f2n \\u0103n k\\u00e8m x\\u00e0 l\\u00e1ch, rau th\\u01a1m v\\u00e0 m\\u1eafm me.<\\/p><p><strong>Mu\\u1ed1i t\\u00f4m<\\/strong><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/h%C5%A9-mu%E1%BB%91i-t%C3%B4m-t%C3%A2y-ninh.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"h\\u0169-mu\\u1ed1i-t\\u00f4m-t\\u00e2y-ninh\\\"><\\/figure><p>Nh\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u1ebfn T\\u00e2y Ninh kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ecf qua m\\u00f3n mu\\u1ed1i t\\u00f4m, \\u0111\\u1eb7c s\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng. C\\u00f4ng d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ee7a mu\\u1ed1i ch\\u1ec9 d\\u00f9ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ea5m c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i tr\\u00e1i c\\u00e2y nh\\u01b0 c\\u00f3c, \\u1ed5i xo\\u00e0i\\u2026 nh\\u01b0ng l\\u1ea1i cu\\u1ed1n h\\u00fat r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u th\\u1ef1c kh\\u00e1ch. Du kh\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u00e2y th\\u01b0\\u1eddng t\\u00ecm mua h\\u0169 mu\\u1ed1i \\u0111em v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u1ec3 d\\u00e0nh ho\\u1eb7c t\\u1eb7ng b\\u1ea1n b\\u00e8, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi th\\u00e2n.<\\/p><p>Nguy\\u00ean li\\u1ec7u c\\u1ee7a m\\u00f3n ch\\u1ea5m \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t n\\u00e0y g\\u1ed3m: mu\\u1ed1i, t\\u00f4m, th\\u1ecbt, t\\u1ecfi, c\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1ecf, \\u1edbt\\u2026 C\\u00e1c nguy\\u00ean li\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u00ednh to\\u00e1n t\\u1ec9 m\\u1ec9 theo li\\u1ec1u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nh\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ecbnh sau \\u0111\\u00f3 \\u0111em xay \\u0111\\u1ec1u r\\u1ed3i rang qua l\\u1eeda v\\u00e0 ph\\u01a1i n\\u1eafng cho mu\\u1ed1i d\\u1eady m\\u00f9i th\\u01a1m.<\\/p><p><strong>&nbsp;Nem b\\u01b0\\u1edfi<\\/strong><\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn3.ivivu.com\\/2020\\/11\\/nem-buoi-Tay-Ninh-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"nem-buoi-Tay-Ninh-1\\\"><\\/figure><p>Nem b\\u01b0\\u1edfi l\\u00e0 m\\u00f3n \\u0103n ch\\u01a1i ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00e2n T\\u00e2y Ninh. Nem b\\u01b0\\u1edfi c\\u00f3 v\\u1ecb chua, m\\u1eb7n, ng\\u1ecdt, v\\u1ecb cay c\\u1ee7a \\u1edbt, ti\\u00eau v\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng th\\u01a1m \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng l\\u00e0m th\\u00e0nh m\\u00f3n nem l\\u1ea1 l\\u1eabm v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea7y d\\u01b0 v\\u1ecb h\\u1ea5p d\\u1eabn.<\\/p><p>Nguy\\u00ean li\\u1ec7u ch\\u00ednh c\\u1ee7a m\\u00f3n \\u0103n n\\u00e0y l\\u00e0 v\\u1ecf b\\u01b0\\u1edfi, \\u0111u \\u0111\\u1ee7 xanh b\\u00e0o nhuy\\u1ec5n ph\\u01a1i kh\\u00f4 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p c\\u00e1c ph\\u1ee5 li\\u1ec7u nh\\u01b0 kh\\u1ebf chua, \\u1edbt hi\\u1ec3m, ti\\u00eau, l\\u00e1 ch\\u00f9m ru\\u1ed9t, l\\u00e1 chu\\u1ed1i\\u2026 Nem ch\\u00edn c\\u00f3 m\\u00e0u h\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0o, c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ed9 dai v\\u1eeba ph\\u1ea3i v\\u00e0 ph\\u1ea3i h\\u1ed9i t\\u1ee5 \\u0111\\u1ee7 c\\u00e1c v\\u1ecb chua, m\\u1eb7n, ng\\u1ecdt, cay, th\\u01a1m\\u2026t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean m\\u1ed9t h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t quy\\u1ebfn r\\u0169 nhi\\u1ec1u th\\u1ef1c kh\\u00e1ch.<br><br><strong>Mang g\\u00ec khi \\u0111i du l\\u1ecbch T\\u00e2y Ninh<\\/strong><\\/p><p>B\\u1ea1n n\\u00ean m\\u1eb7c qu\\u1ea7n \\u00e1o g\\u1ecdn nh\\u1eb9, d\\u1ec5 v\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, mang \\u00e1o kho\\u00e1c, m\\u0169, kem ch\\u1ed1ng n\\u1eafng, kem ch\\u1ed1ng mu\\u1ed7i, thu\\u1ed1c tr\\u1ecb c\\u00f4n tr\\u00f9ng, thu\\u1ed1c \\u0111au b\\u1ee5ng (\\u0111\\u1ec1 ph\\u00f2ng khi th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c c\\u00e1c m\\u00f3n l\\u1ea1). N\\u00ean mang gi\\u00e0y th\\u1ec3 thao hay gi\\u00e0y b\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ec3 leo n\\u00fai, v\\u00e0 c\\u1ea7m theo b\\u1ed9 kim, ch\\u1ec9, n\\u00fat \\u00e1o, kim b\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u1ec1 ph\\u00f2ng c\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p b\\u1ea5t ng\\u1edd. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, n\\u1ebfu c\\u00f3 d\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ecbnh d\\u00e3 ngo\\u1ea1i v\\u00e0 qua \\u0111\\u00eam tr\\u00ean n\\u00fai B\\u00e0 \\u0110en th\\u00ec ph\\u1ea3i trang b\\u1ecb l\\u1ec1u, \\u00e1o \\u1ea5m, th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n\\u2026<\\/p>\",\"thumbnail\":\"2020-Nov-Fri_1605886025569.jpg\",\"isdeleted\":false,\"status\":false,\"hot\":\"on\",\"province_id\":\"3\",\"created_by\":2,\"updated_by\":2,\"id\":11}', 'http://localhost:8080/DATN/public/admin/news', '::1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/87.0.4280.66 Safari/537.36', NULL, '2020-11-20 08:27:05', '2020-11-20 08:27:05'),
